    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/5b168cb4bf2df3de178f974e8a222fb9.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Braise</strong> 是一款设定在奇幻世界中的叙事冒险游戏。玩家将扮演一名年轻女性，调查她祖母的失踪以及一头陷入疯狂的龙的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索龙之谷，完成任务和解谜，揭开隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/75a53f076e5f3cad29bb24e339b350d1.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验引人入胜的故事和令人喜爱的角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个龙与人类刚刚建立起脆弱和平的世界中，您将追寻失踪祖母的线索——她是一位著名的勇士。然而，当她的龙陷入疯狂时，山谷的宁静被打破，而一个神秘的教派似乎在暗中操控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/2e272388338944b4cf1630ddb3647210.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了揭开所有的秘密，您需要彻底探查整个山谷！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从河流到神庙，再到地下城，龙之谷中有各种各样的地点，这些地方充满了可以发现的物品，帮助您推进冒险进程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/f580339e45a85635160abdfe561fe187.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成山谷居民的任务，解决谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您需要运用逻辑和创造力来解开谜题。无论是通过组合物品，还是观察环境中的隐藏线索，每个谜题都会让您更深入地体验这个奇幻世界的丰富内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.poster.avif?t=1766177770\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.webm?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324930/extras/77d8c73fe04cf52859364842cc2b23d2.mp4?t=1766177770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找鱼饵和最佳的钓鱼点，探索河流中所有种类的鱼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供大约 1.5 到 2 小时的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于游戏：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由一人开发。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一个电子游戏项目。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一年开发周期。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘像素艺术，无人工智能参与。</p></li></ul>",
